                  "Value": "ISO symbol, If you are pregnant, have circulatory problems, osteoarthritis, rheumatism or diabetes, consult a doctor before use.  Do not use if you are hypersensitive or insensitive to heat or cold. Do not use with pain-relieving creams or ointments. Every person perceives cold or heat differently. Therefore, always follow your own feelings. Heat only in the microwave. Settings may vary depending on your microwave. Do not use if the HotCold Pack is leaking. If spilled, avoid contact with skin, eyes and mouth. In case of contact, rinse immediately with water. Use with children only under adult supervision. Never place the HotCold Pack directly on the skin. Keep out of reach of children."
